message.body: Hi there, how are you? And what does your username mean?
Hi! I'm doing well, yourself? And it means "cradle song" so...essentially lullaby.
I'm doing well too, I have friends in town and we're exploring :) I knew it had something to do with music - I sing opera from time to time and -lied looked familiar
Very nice! I honestly miss my choir. :'(
It was my high school choir and my youth opera. We went everywhere; Scotland, Ireland, Germany, etc. Honestly miss it; was like a second family.
That sounds great - must have been a great choir!!
